data.description:
*** $2,500 incentive for buyers closing plus seller paying title ***

Discover the epitome of modern living in this meticulously crafted sanctuary tucked away in a serene cul-de-sac location. Seamlessly blending luxury with functionality, this residence offers an array of desirable features, including integrated ceiling speakers with a Bluetooth-enabled head unit for effortless entertainment, a convenient stairway entrance to the attic providing ample storage space, and an HVAC system equipped with a UV light filter to ensure pristine air quality, ideal for those with sensitivities. Security is paramount with a comprehensive system including live monitoring cameras, providing peace of mind. Situated just 15 minutes from the vibrant stock yards and the electrifying Cowboys and Rangers stadiums, this home offers both convenience and excitement, promising a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication.
